{
  "texts": [
    "To the best of our knowledge, no surveys have been done exclusively on NED.",
    "The survey from Balog [17] in 2018 defined the problems of EL, NER and NED.",
    "The author concludes by presenting the general process of EL, which is only composed of both NER and NED.",
    "The authors affirm that the named entities have to be extracted before being disambiguated.",
    "The author also focuses on both NER and NED by citing some pertinent research in both areas."
  ]
}